com.pfc.android.archcomponent.adapters

Class DataAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v7.widget.RecyclerView.Adapter<DataAdapter.Holder>
      • com.pfc.android.archcomponent.adapters.DataAdapter

  • public class DataAdapter
extends android.support.v7.widget.RecyclerView.Adapter<DataAdapter.Holder>
    DataAdapter extends RecyclerView.Adapter

    This Adapter is in charge of the interface elements that are showing in every recycler view for the listfragment. Because your adapter subclasses RecyclerView.Adapter, you need to add the following methods:

    • 1.- getItemCount()
    • 2.- onCreateViewHolder(ViewGroup parent, int viewType)
    • 3.- onBindViewHolder(Holder holder, int position)

    1.0
